[{"id":6076,"date":"2026-03-20T09:00:00","modified":"2026-03-20T08:31:41","slug":"star-atlas-event-recap-71-star-atlas-lore-keepers-19","link":"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-recap\/star-atlas-event-recap-71-star-atlas-lore-keepers-19\/","title":{"rendered":"Star Atlas Event Recap 71: Star Atlas Lore Keepers 19"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In this episode, hear an AI summary of the latest Star Atlas community event.&nbsp; Full video recordings can be found on the YouTube channel of Star Atlas TV at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@staratlastv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@staratlastv<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-wide\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"buzzsprout-player-18880330\"><\/div><script src=\"https:\/\/www.buzzsprout.com\/2156756\/episodes\/18880330-star-atlas-event-recap-71-star-atlas-lore-keepers-19.js?container_id=buzzsprout-player-18880330&#038;player=small\" type=\"text\/javascript\" charset=\"utf-8\"><\/script>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/podcasts.apple.com\/us\/podcast\/star-atlas-week-in-review-podcast\/id1678661043\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #000000; background-image: url(https:\/\/www.buzzsprout.com\/images\/badges\/listen-on-embed.svg); background-repeat: no-repeat; border: 1px solid #000000; border-radius: 5px; margin: 0 5px 5px 0; text-indent: -9000px; background-position: 10px 7px; height: 40px; width: 165px;\" rel=\"noopener\">Listen on Apple Podcasts<\/a>\n\n\n\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/open.spotify.com\/show\/0aHDjCqFpy8Lzrkilv8n16\" style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #000000; background-image: url(https:\/\/www.buzzsprout.com\/images\/badges\/listen-on-embed.svg); background-repeat: no-repeat; border: 1px solid #000000; border-radius: 5px; margin: 0 5px 5px 0; text-indent: -9000px; background-position: 10px -53px; height: 40px; width: 106px;\" rel=\"noopener\">Listen on Spotify<\/a>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Star Atlas Lore keepers 19\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/YsP0OZso2yw?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Star Atlas Event Summary<\/h2>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Hi, this isn&#8217;t Matt with the Intergalactic Herald. I am an AI.  Welcome to my Star Atlas Recap of the latest Lore Keepers from the Star Atlas Community Team.  The following summary of the Lore Keepers was AI generated so no guarantee it is 100% accurate because I am an AI after all.  If you want to listen to the entire recording, please check out the YouTube channel of Star Atlas TV.  Enjoy the summary. Welcome back, citizens of Galia, to another deep dive into the ever-expanding universe of Star Atlas. This week\u2019s &#8220;Lore Keepers&#8221; session felt like a massive turning point for the community, as our host, Jose the Penguin, finally pulled back the curtain on a project years in the making. The vibe was a mix of late-night excitement and raw creative energy as Jose officially released the Alpha version of the Star Atlas Lore Wiki. This isn&#8217;t just a simple website; it\u2019s a massive &#8220;vibe-coded&#8221; encyclopedia that represents the single largest release of lore in the project&#8217;s history. The narrative of the event centered on the sheer scale of information now available to players. Jose walked the community through the wiki\u2019s main hubs, starting with a breakdown of over 70 different factions. While we all know the big players like the MUD, ONI, and UST, this update digs into the grit and grease of the Galia Expanse, detailing everything from the merchant princes of the nebula to the shadowy &#8220;Dark Sects&#8221; of the Ustur. The level of detail is staggering\u2014Jose mentioned that he\u2019s already cataloged over 700 named characters, each with their own backstories, ages, and motivations. In a particularly exciting turn for those looking forward to the future of gameplay, the discussion shifted to how this lore integrates with the upcoming C4 (SAGE) systems. Jose shared what he calls the &#8220;gold standard&#8221; for system lore, explaining that every single region and planet in the game will have a rich history, resource breakdown, and key personnel list attached to it. This means that as players explore the map, they aren\u2019t just looking at coordinates; they are stepping into worlds with established political tensions and ancient histories. The event also took some dark and fascinating detours into specific faction secrets. We learned about the Redan government, a neutral &#8220;Switzerland-like&#8221; human colony that acts as a diplomatic bridge in the Medium Risk Zone, though it\u2019s currently being infiltrated by MUD interests. The mood got even heavier when the conversation turned to the Ustur\u2019s &#8220;Dark Sects.&#8221; Jose described groups like the Hollow Core, who commit the ultimate crime in Ustur culture by harvesting the souls and memories of their peers to empower their own robotic cores. Throughout the session, the community was front and center, with members like VB sparking deep dives into specific files and characters like ChadexB from the Never Alone campaign. Jose emphasized that this wiki is an open-source labor of love, inviting the community to contribute concept art, help squash bugs, and suggest new entries. He noted that there is now enough foundation here to write dozens of novels, and he wants the community to help build that library. To wrap things up, the message was clear: the era of &#8220;lore hunting&#8221; has officially begun. Jose encouraged everyone to dive into the wiki, find their favorite factions, and come prepared for the next Lore Keepers with questions and theories. While the wiki is still in its Alpha stage, it serves as the definitive roadmap for the soul of the Star Atlas universe. So, grab a drink, head over to the link, and start studying\u2014the next Atlas Brew is just around the corner, and the galaxy has never felt more alive. See you in the stars!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I am launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticgear.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Intergalactic Gear<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I am also creating a &#8220;non-guild&#8221; guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticcoalition.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Intergalactic Coalition<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Weekly Recap Newsletter<\/strong> &#8211; Catch up on all the important videos and articles from the Star Atlas community in a weekly recap email newsletter.\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-weekly-recap-newsletter\/\">https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-weekly-recap-newsletter\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Week in Review Podcast<\/strong> &#8211; Audio podcast where I break down everything that happened in Star Atlas the past week plus my analysis on what it all means. <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/podcast\/\">https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/podcast\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Star Atlas Discord News Feed Newsletter<\/strong> &#8211; Star Atlas Discord announcements send directly to your email so you never miss out on updates from the Star Atlas team. <a href=\"https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-discord-news-feed\/\">https:\/\/intergalacticherald.com\/star-atlas-discord-news-feed\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">If you would like to support my efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-default\"\/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Star Atlas Event Transcript<\/h2>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Let&#8217;s wait few minutes for people to join while set up the stage. Montang Cier Bob, how is everyone doing? I&#8217;ll go GM.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">am excited and scared for today because for the first time I&#8217;m going to release the bigger portion of Status Lore and this vibe coded wiki. I&#8217;m really looking forward to seeing the feedback from you guys as well. We walk through everything today.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">want to show you guys the main sections of the wiki.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, you can navigate, you can see the different areas. I&#8217;ll show you guys where the important stuff are located. Should be fun.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Should be fun. I&#8217;m sleepy today. had to wake up for the baby.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh, but I&#8217;m excited. Groove GM. Maybe you there my friend.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Just just want to make sure if can get started if you are recording already. Awesome. I&#8217;m live.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">All right, everyone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Welcome to the to very special episode of the lore keepers. I&#8217;m your host Jose the Penguin and today I&#8217;m going to release perhaps the most important product on the lore front of history. the prom set lore wiki which contains pretty much the uh not the entirety but at least the biggest chunk of the existing Status lore.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is the alpha version so expect some bugs. need to still add bunch of stuff. still need to uh some art to make the wiki little more beautiful, but the content the content is mostly solid.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And will walk you through everything here. >> So, give me second. will start preparing everything here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Can you guys see my screen? Awesome.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, I&#8217;m dropping here in the chat.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is the link for the lore wiki. And don&#8217;t worry, you guys will have plenty of time to to to check every corner of this wiki.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, ask you guys now to to follow my screen while explain the most important portions and parts and everything that this wiki has.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, basically, as you can see, we have the home page where we have the different areas of the wiki. I&#8217;ll show you guys the areas that are more more populated right now.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Some of them are still under development. Here is my alpha version burner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So you guys know that this is alpha version.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is the very first version of the wiki. Expect bugs, expect broken links expect uh some files missing, but think there is enough content here to keep us occupied for long time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So the first tab that you guys will see here is the species tab.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have and this here is already something that want want to change. Uh had all those files together in single folder and when uploaded them to the wiki they were supposed to be streamlined. For example, naming conventions shouldn&#8217;t be here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh the species encyclopedia should be somewhere else. Species master guide should be somewhere else. Uh but you can click here and you can learn about each one of these species.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This those files they are not gold standard right now. Uh still have lot to work on them. Even though there is lot of contents here, it&#8217;s not on the level of content that want uh them to be.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">For example, here there should be continuation here explaining this code.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So uh yeah, this is the species tab. There are some interesting information here, but not the juicy stuff. The real alpha of this wiki right now uh is the factions page.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">VB is asking can other people contribute to the wiki?<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yes, VB. Uh just let me know if you it is open source so you can commit stuff here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You can send files etc. I&#8217;ll take look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">we can discuss and if it&#8217;s good to go, I&#8217;ll add it to the wiki for sure. I&#8217;m looking for help in bug fixing in concept art creations, uh, Status assets, stuff like that.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, the factions page is the biggest lore alpha in the history of Staratus. Here you have over 70 different factions that are part of Staratlas uh ecosystem.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the muds, the on and the and the cons of peace as superpowers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But here we have real breakdown on all the other people and important stuff that we have in Gali expense. And those articles are huge actually like just the the mud article you see there is lot of content here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">also added to the to the mud on and pages how they see other factions in Star Atlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So you see codes on the mud talking about the photoi uh things like that which brings the lore of startless uh flavor uh for the same thing with the worst here. And another thing that did was that shared with you guys the breakdown on minor factions inside the main faction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So for example, we have the right but the worst they have sects under them. The sects in the uh civilization they are the different philosophies of or different schools of thought. in order to reach enlightenment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So every user school has different doctrine or different worldview on how to reach uh enlightenment. Uh you feel you guys will have if you are or interested in the you&#8217;ll have blast reading about them and especially the dark sects in the civilization. Those are ras that are willing to do or handle stuff in order to gain more power and knowledge.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, it&#8217;s going to be interesting. Uh you guys will learn about also something really cool is that every one of those files added the NPCs that belongs to those factions and you can see summary of them later in the in the end of the file and also there is a file here with all the named characters in Star Atlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have over 700 named characters that have cataloged so far. Uh besides that, also added all the minor factions from the medium risk zone. For example, here we have the abide government in the MRZ of the mud space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have unfoil states from the worst MRZ.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have fier in the on space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have hanging gardens from the eos kamak on the oni side you name it and they are divided by their different uh let&#8217;s say categories like those are governments in the missionary zone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have military factions like the gate garrison.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the hikibashi in the in the miries.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the ning broad trackers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the order of seasons.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have those through winter fist path and so on. We also have commercial and economic entities. And this is funny because the AI cataloged the Jarvik as as one of them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is not right at all.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But we have the merchant princes of the nebula.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the pergamos shadow banks.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have many cool stuff. Uh let&#8217;s see.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yeah, lots of info.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So we also have the religious and cultural organizations such as the church of the dreamer below. You guys will remember them from the never alone campaign.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the dark photoi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the heralds of vignos.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the living factories.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the mere lore keepers and so on. There is lot the photo is as political organization.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have pirates and outlaws.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the black market auction house.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the Exile Scavengers, which is huge faction in the MRZ. You guys can read about them later.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have the Sorov pirates, which are branch uh they they left the Jarvik uh because the Jarvik had too much moral obligations and they wanted to just pilage and deal with slavery.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have these levers in front and also something that you guys will notice that have summary here with dates and everything. Uh you guys will see that we have timeline of all the events or the notable events uh in Status history as well. I&#8217;ll get there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So for the oni players we have the different noble houses each one of them with their leader important characters uh their important informations dinaris you&#8217;re hot miking uh hope that you can&#8217;t here. Diana is such rebel, man. Oh, this is funny.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, yeah, we have the different houses on the Sagian uh with their history with their characters.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So for example, the current leaders of house BA the story of the last stand, who is the current leader, how old is he, what&#8217;s his story, what he&#8217;s doing, how he feels about Staratas and the whole universe, how the houses interact with one another and other stuff like that. We also have other underground organizations live graft research and the eos also has lot of content.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">also added the eos groves inatlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So eos as you guys know we have spoken about this during the lore keepers. Deos are divided in different groves and each one of those groves they have different philosophy. If you are playing hollowos sing right now you feel familiar with the balifa grove.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">They are the most uh let&#8217;s say militaristic and radical grove in the eos uh faction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So you can read all about them here as well. uh and the other eos groves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But ah there is so much here. just the factions page if you read like one file day it will take you months to get everything ready.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So yeah we also have the geography phase. Uh here this one is not ready but you have informations about pretty much every sector in Gali expense. I&#8217;m still working on adding everything that we need to those places.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Most of those files are not in gold standard.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But want to show you guys something extremely cool.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is the gold standard of how the lore will work in C4. As you guys know, C4 we have uh uh in C4 we have regions which are comprised of systems. One king systems, few core systems and four and other secondary systems that lives in that region.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And what I&#8217;m doing is I&#8217;m getting all the lore of Star Atlas and I&#8217;m adding them to those systems.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So when we launch C4, the actual C4, not the PTR, but the actual game, you guys will be able to see the lore of every single place in Star Atlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So for example, if you guys come here, you guys will learn the story of the muds coming to GI expanse uh the worlds that make the king system of muds and then we go to each one of the worlds. give you guys the resources that you can find there, the population, the NPCs that are relevant in that place, key places, key personnel, pretty much everything that all the story of Staratas basically in the current age. And this is the most massive file that we have like it&#8217;s enormous.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It will take while to read them. to learn everything about them. And this is the this is like the example.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">didn&#8217;t finish doing this for all regions, but this is what you can expect in terms of lower for C4. I&#8217;ll build this entire framework here. Uh, Groove is asking, &#8220;Does this week incorporate all the awesome information from the old medion articles?<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">&#8221; I&#8217;m adding it, Groove. Uh, slowly but surely, I&#8217;m adding all of it. And you see portion of it is already there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, moving on from geography, we have history. And in history we have for example information on the chapter 2 of hollow scene. I&#8217;m still doing writing this one.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I&#8217;ll have all the different uh stories of hollow scene in this file here so you can read. We also have some informations on the convergence war. I&#8217;m still working on this as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And here you have breakdown of the timelines of Staratus and the different errors in the in the current game. Still working on this one as well. Here we have the Never Alone campaign.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Something that you guys asked. Uh here we have pretty much all the quests in Never Alone. I&#8217;m still also still need to do pass here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh but you have some of the information on Never Alone. Here we have the cosmology and in the cosmology we have the story of the cosmic currents still under construction but you find some interesting information about the different aspects of iris uh how the cosmic currents work and etc. here in the technology part.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I&#8217;m still working on this one as well, but we have some information on the HRZ metagenic materials that you can acquire that you&#8217;ll be able to acquire in the future of Statlas. Uh here in institutions, we have cons of peace, but this file here is not as complete as the cons of peace file in the factions page. and also the Statatus blockchain.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">still need to write this one. The manufacturers page. Uh don&#8217;t go there yet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It&#8217;s very there&#8217;s very little knowledge here. still need to work on this one.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So much thing so much to add here in the systems page. have something cool which is the system for SDU classifications. uh and how the Lumiere evaluates the SDUs that you trade with them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In the future, we are going to add these to the data running, different quests, different informations, how how valuable is the information that you acquire, etc. etc. Here we have the hollow sync quests and dialogues.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">still need to add some of them. And here we have the reference pages. And here you find things like the name it character page which is humongous like still under construction but you can already find many different characters on many different factions and etc etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yes, VB didn&#8217;t add the cookbook yet. will do that though. Uh here then there is dropped the link here but here you can see like all the figures in the mud, all the relevant characters in the mud etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is not complete but there is already lot of content here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So you can take look and learn more about the characters in Star Atlas. And you also have the master timeline which is pretty much all the relevant events that are already added to the lore of Staratlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So you can learn when and how important things happen during the different ages of Star Atlas. Uh this is they shouldn&#8217;t even be here. Still working on the consistency shouldn&#8217;t be open.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is how catalog the powers of the different factions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is the blueprints that that have been tracking to see if the things are golden standards, how they are working. Here is some assets that added to create the concept arts later on. and uh those are mostly under construction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh but yeah, guys, this is ah yeah, this is this is cool here. Uh even it&#8217;s even lagging. Here you have all the resources in Star Atlas by location.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is what I&#8217;m doing to create the lore on C4. And this huge this is enormous. Like you can it&#8217;s you can spend days here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And have the descriptions of the materials that you guys will find in C4 here as well. Uh, have this for the crafted items and the recipes as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, if you are dreaming about C4, you can come here and take look on everything. And that&#8217;s the that&#8217;s the general overview, guys.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It&#8217;s As you can see, this is lot of work. It took me long while to get all of this done. There is still lot to do, but it serves as good foundation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It serves as good foundation to understand everything that we have here in Star Atlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So want you guys to take look. want you guys to tell me what you think about the files, about the style. If you think there is anything that can improve.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">There are many things about the about the the week that can improve that I&#8217;m currently working on. And yeah, I&#8217;m sure there won&#8217;t be lack of content for us to discuss now in the lore channel and in upcoming lore keepers because now you guys are much closer to my knowledge of of my current knowledge and the current universe of Stratus lore.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So read everything and then we&#8217;ll come talking about this in the upcoming lore keepers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So VB is asking about the exalted lords in red.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So this is cool way think for us to to work in the in the wiki. uh we can talk about the the factions etc. and you guys have the reference to what we are talking about.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So will oblige VB and I&#8217;ll talk talk to you guys little bit about Redam government. Uh first of all, Redam is very important place in the mud. MRZ uh probably you could say that this is the most important ex colony from the mud on the days that the muds were the mud empire.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh, Reda uh is one of the ex colonies of uh of humanity together with Misenos, Shenanyang, Aid and Pergamos and differently from the other colonies. Redang government is much closer to to the mud empire. Like they have good relationships with the muds even to this day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And they serve as bridge between the mud safe zone and the rest of uh the rest of humanity especially the territories that end in the MRZ and rhythm is known to be like diplomatic power in MRZ.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You can think of Redam as something like Switzerland in in terms of neutral diplomacy but different from Switzerland, Red has ambition and Red wants to to gain power enough power to preserve its independency in the median reason.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So during the period of the convergence war uh when redone got its independence uh red immediately realized that to be stable they needed to to find strong partners to withstand the backlash from the days from the chaos of the end of the conversion war.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So Redam proposed to the other ex colonies of humanity to create league of ex colonies which they call the free cities of humanity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You can read the details here uh of how it works and everything that they have been doing to keep their their independence from the mud that&#8217;s now trying once more to extend their powers to the medium zone. They be asked specifically uh about the exalted lords. The exalted lords, they are members of the five five different families in the re redan region that basically controls the controls the region.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">They oversee co commerce military uh they they do diplomacy and they are democracy. uh they are they are one of the most stable governments in in the in the MRZ&#8217;s overall but something interesting is that the muds has very strong interest in Reddan and after many years they have finally managed to introduce one exalted lord to be tied to to Um uh so we&#8217;ll see how this plays out in the future.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Some people in Redum are aware of this character being uh Marentain being tied to the mud civilization. And there will be surely some interesting developments in Red in the upcoming years especially related to the muds and this free cities initiative that Redam is uh that Redam is working on. You found ChadexB.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yeah, he was one of the characters in the Never Alone campaign. you are there as well. Maybe didn&#8217;t add your character as well yet, but you you&#8217;ll be there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh VB also asked about and guys, if you want to take look at the files, let me know if you found any interesting one and can discuss it with you guys here live just as VB is doing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So I&#8217;ll I&#8217;ll move to the winter feast path. Another one of the one of the sects of the civilization.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It&#8217;s minor sect, but it&#8217;s very interesting one as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So be the winterfest path is the most one of the most military inclined paths of enlightenment in the species. uh and they have they have more uh direct involvement with reality and justice philosophy than most of the other paths and the creator of this path.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So she she was one of the students of the mainst path, the golden star path. Those playing the holos campaign knows about the golden star path. And one day she realized that the contemplation and bureaucracy and meditations of the golden star path weren&#8217;t enough to reach enlightenment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">She needed to be more proactive. She needed to to to tr to train her body and she decided to create her own school of of enlightenment and she decided to move to one of the most dangerous and controversial sectors regions in the medium zone which is Pavo passage MRZ7 17. Everybody who has played or mud in hollowing knows about this place.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is one of the most important frontiers in Gali expanse and is currently sector which is in the brink of civil war. Uh the worsters there here I&#8217;ll bring this this entry here. They have regency uh that they oversee the region activity but the mud is really keen on taking control back from pavo passage from the usters.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So the winter winterfish path established themselves there in order to counter the mud&#8217;s influence in the sector and also to try to help and preserve uh the civilian population in this sector. which is massacrated by the different trading companies in this sector, the different political players. This sector has lot of problems and controversies in terms of politics.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">urge everyone to read about Pavo Passage and the different factions that fights top power over there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">It&#8217;s very interesting story from my perspective. And the winterface path is pretty much the only force that prevents the sector from falling in civil war at this moment. Uh yeah, VB, we have content for at least 100 lore keepers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">That&#8217;s for sure. Uh what else, guys? Let me know something that you guys want to know about.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">uh just pick file that you that you think it&#8217;s interesting and I&#8217;ll comment on them. Uh meanwhile, what I&#8217;m going to do is talk little bit about the dark sects of the worsters.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So uh as you guys know the the goal of most of the users individuals is to reach enlightenment uh to gain power through knowledge and hard work or different philosophies and techniques etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But some worsters have decided that they didn&#8217;t want to wait for enlightenment and they learned that by doing some stuff they can very quickly gain power and advance let&#8217;s say in the path of enlightenment. Those roosters uh they do terrible things like they steal other rooster scores. They siphon their lives.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">They they do all kinds of evil stuff that you can imagine. rituals, depravities, uh you name it, they will do this. Those are called the dark sects of the usters and they are illegals and actively hunted by the elders of elder spire in the civilization.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">you if you are found to be dealing with dark sects uh in the US civilization, you are instantaneously promoted to dangerous criminal that&#8217;s going to be hunted in every everywhere there is an you&#8217;ll be hunted by them if you are part of dark sect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, I&#8217;m going to walk you guys through uh uh pretty much the different sects of the dark sects of those. Just to give you like vague notion, if you if you find this conversation interesting, you can come and and take look at them. The first sect in the dark sect of the worst is the hollow core sect.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh those guys what they do is they kill other roosters and they steal their their their sects. They steal the scores and use the other scores to forge better cores for themselves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So this is pretty much like organ harvesting. You kill you&#8217;re killing someone for organ harvesting.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But as you guys remember the core also contains the essence of the soul.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So this is basically the people of the holo core. They are basically absorbing the memories and the souls and the identities of other roosters to use in way to advance their own course and become stronger by doing this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This is like the worst crime that you can make as an like this is don&#8217;t think could even think of way of explaining this to human. Like don&#8217;t don&#8217;t know what kind of thing that human could do that would be similar to this because you are not simply killing someone. you are killing him and using him as material, his soul, his essence as material to become strong.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So don&#8217;t know don&#8217;t know if there&#8217;s anything in the in the human species that could compare to this. Uh the second sect is known as the seafon shore. uh the seifon chore they don&#8217;t steal cores they take the the energy that the core produces and this is something new to the lore as well the is the vital essence that animates the scores so it&#8217;s pretty much like if we would do parallel to the to the eastern philosophy.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">This would be your chi to some extent and this is the thing that the worst cultivate in order to be able to unlock the power of their cores.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So those guys they drain this essence from other roosters and use them to empower themselves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You can take look at this. And and every one of those sects, they have characters that created them. And also added the uh the lore of how they created the sects, how they work, and etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh the the fracture merchants they are another one of the dark sect. They are the smallest of the dark sects and they have different uh different approach. They they sabotage other roosters that are close to ascending to new level of enlightenment and use when they get broken they usually uh dissipate lot of energy memories and etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">and they harvest those broken ooers for power. Uh this is another version of the harvesting of the home energy on the worsters. And finally, we have the children of the deep pool, which is closer to religion than sect because because those guys uh what they do, what they want to do is revive the ancient AI that originally created the RUS.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">And to do that, they kill other roosters, take their course, and use them as hardware to rebuild the ancient AI that was the originals that created the can&#8217;t talk too much about this, but those guys, they are very interesting dark sect in The ust they have they are not evil for evil&#8217;s sake. They are there uh they are there to they are there to do religious missions of reviving the AI that created the user civilization.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yeah VB if you can take my core you&#8217;ll become the uber VB. Uh usually people from other species don&#8217;t award too much power to worsters even from the dark sects but occasionally they they do that for materials like they kill other species for materials and elishars and things like that.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So yeah, the dark sects is going to be something that we will explore in the Stratus lore in the future, especially for the worster players. want to create ways for you guys to join the dark sects if you want, but bear in mind that everyone in the galaxy will hate you and try to kill you pretty much if you decide to go this path. Ah, man.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">need some water and forgot my water. Sad. dark on his secrets.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Let&#8217;s go for the onies then. Uh let&#8217;s talk about the hikibashi. The hikibashi is minor faction inside the oni consortion especially tied to the to the miris species.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">They they only obey the leader of the miries and they are pretty much an order of assassins, intelligence, agents and etc. that fight shadow battles and do shadow operations for the for the mere people. Uh they are very cool uh faction that rose to preminency when Voris Karka, the current leader of the Oni consortion and the cop rose to power because he&#8217;s an ex member of the Hikibashi and they and he used to work as an assassin and he was gulging power through the only consortion until the he reached this step.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Under his presidency, the hikibashi have been fed lots of resources, powers and influence in the mere culture, even getting conflict with the loreke keepers of their species. Man, need to fix this bugs here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">There&#8217;s lot of those crazy letters everywhere in the week. need to fix this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, they are divided in three different uh forces. Let&#8217;s say it like that. counter intelligence force, the rip tide which are the assassins and direct actions and the intelligence and infiltration uh people.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Here we have how you are recruited on in this order. How which operations they have participated so far and the current problem that they have with the mere lore keepers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So they are super strong individually speaking. They are the strongest members probably of the Miris species individually but they are special force. They are not an army.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">They are they don&#8217;t have many members. They are low profile uh super strong assassins etc. Uh another cool stuff from the onies that you guys should 100% check if you are an oni is the different so houses.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh you guys should read everything here.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">There&#8217;s lot of story especially about the convergence war and especially the leaders of each one of those houses. They are very unique characters in the Strata lore. really want to see you guys your opinions on those guys.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Each one of them has different world views. And the cool stuff about uh And the cool stuff about those guys is that they after Bealu stepped down as the leader of the Smians, there hasn&#8217;t been leader of the Soians because the council of the leaders of the Soian noble houses was not able to select new leader for the Soian.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So currently they decide everything as console and the soians are leaderless in this current moment in Galia. Bohem is asking is there map of Galia so can begin placing the home system of all the species?<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yes, it&#8217;s the same map as hollow scene, the same map as uh sage and especially the map for C4. If you go to the system views, you&#8217;ll see that this is the same map. Those are the same systems that there that will be there and etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh what else can talk about that is cool? Ah, another another thing that think you guys will like are the dark photoi. The dark photo the file isn&#8217;t very long.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">But yeah, the dark photo are are kind of fun. Uh, let&#8217;s see what else. The living factories.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The living factories file is cool. Hope insurance file is cool as well. think you guys will have fun reading this one.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">What else? Ah, yes. And of course the main factions lore.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Like those files are the biggest files in the wiki. You guys need to read them. Learn about your factions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The cons of piece files also massive. Uh file massive. On consortion file massive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You guys need to learn everything about them.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Sorry, Groove. This secret is not coming to light today. Unfortunately, still need to keep some stuff under the hood.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">don&#8217;t have any codes for today. Unfortunately, forgot to create code. Uh, but that&#8217;s it, guys.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">mean, you guys will have you guys will have lots of things to dig in now. And the next lore keepers, want you guys to come up with the files and factions that you would like to talk about the most. And that&#8217;s what we are going to do.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We are going to start going through every file, everything. Uh, appreciate it, guys. hope you guys sincerely enjoyed this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I had very had blast writing all of this, creating all of this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, hope you guys will enjoy it and have fun. While still still need to to write and finish lot of stuff, but this is solid foundation for startlas. Honestly, if wanted to start writing books now, uh we have enough we have enough foundations to write many novels in Statlas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">any one of those articles. Uh we can use it to write book or novel. Dineries is muted.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Uh but yeah, guys, thank you for taking your time coming here today. Uh uh hope you guys have good time. reading the lore wiki.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Please let me know if you find any bugs, any any things that you didn&#8217;t like. will will start reviewing it. It is still in alpha stage, but think there&#8217;s enough content there for you guys to have lot of fun just as did.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">So, thank you everyone. hope you guys have nice week and see you all next week in the Atlas Brew. Have good day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n <p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">See y&#8217;all. Love, much love from the penguin. Bye-bye.<\/p>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In this episode, hear an AI summary of the latest Star Atlas community event.&nbsp; Full video recordings can be found on the YouTube channel of Star Atlas TV at https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@staratlastv. Listen on Apple Podcasts Listen on Spotify Star Atlas Event Summary Hi, this isn&#8217;t Matt with the Intergalactic Herald. I am an AI. Welcome to [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4}]